verbose_text: Analysis of pre and mature miRNA levels of over-expressing NF90a and NF45 cells showed that in four out of the ten miRNAs (miR-185, miR-21, miR-23b and miR-34a), the pre-miRNA levels were elevated or unchanged whereas the mature levels were decreased (XREF_FIG).
evidence: levels of over-expressing NF90a and NF45
